data.description: Welcome to your next investment! This 2960 sqft gem features a spacious 4/2.5 layout with an open concept. Roof and HVAC units replaced in 2022! The downstairs primary bedroom has a large bathroom with a separate bathtub and shower leading to a walk-in closet. Upstairs, there are 3 additional bedrooms and a generous-sized loft.  Outside, you will find a relaxing, oversized covered patio. This home sits on a nice-sized corner lot. Selling As-Is, please see additional documents for the foundation report. It is an ideal location near schools and shopping, making it a great opportunity!
